Package: metagene
Version: 2.3.6
Date: 2014-05-05
Title: A package to produce metagene plots
Author: Charles Joly Beauparlant <charles.joly-beauparlant@crchul.ulaval.ca>,
    Fabien Claude Lamaze <fabien.lamaze.1@ulaval.ca>, Rawane Samb
